org.modelio.metamodel.uml.infrastructure

Interface TagParameter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<MObject>, Element, MObject

    public interface TagParameter
extends Element
    TagParameter v0.0.9054 TaggedValues are a powerful mechanism in Modelio. They can have Parameters that must conform to the TagType structure. TagParameters belong to their TaggedValue.
